    <string name="rules_gameplay">GAMEPLAY</string>
    <string name="rules_text">1- Players are randomly assigned roles such as Vampire, Villager, Sheriff, Doctor, Watcher.\n\n2- At night, Vampires and the Serial Killer choose targets; other special roles use their abilities.\n\n3- During the day, players discuss to identify the guilty and hold a vote.\n\n4- Villagers win if all Vampires and Serial Killers are eliminated; Vampires win if all Villagers are gone. The Serial Killer\'s goal is to be the last one standing.\n\nExtra: The Plus package includes additional roles like Saboteur, Coroner, Veteran, Madman, and Wizard.\n\nNote: The app manages the entire process, no moderator needed.</string>
